\\"This library exports OpenTelemetry span data to a Zipkin-compatible backend using the Zipkin reporter. By default it sends spans in Zipkin JSON format over HTTP to a configured endpoint, with support for alternate encodings or custom senders.\\\",\\nmetadata/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-exporter-zipkin/index.json:37:    \\\"source-code-url\\\" : \\\"https://repo1.maven.org/maven2/io/opentelemetry/opentelemetry-exporter-zipkin/$version$/opentelemetry-exporter-zipkin-$version$-sources.jar\\\",\\nmetadata/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-exporter-zipkin/index.json:38:    \\\"repository-url\\\" : \\\"https://github.com/open-telemetry/opentelemetry-java\\\",\\nmetadata/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-exporter-zipkin/index.json:39:    \\\"test-code-url\\\" : \\\"https://github.com/open-telemetry/opentelemetry-java/tree/v$version$/exporters/zipkin/src/test\\\",\\nmetadata/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-exporter-zipkin/index.json:40:    \\\"documentation-url\\\" : \\\"https://github.com/open-telemetry/opentelemetry-java/blob/v$version$/exporters/zipkin/README.md\\\",\\nmetadata/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-exporter-zipkin/index.json:41:    \\\"description\\\" : \\\"This library exports OpenTelemetry span data to a Zipkin-compatible backend using the Zipkin reporter. By default it sends spans in Zipkin format over HTTP and can be configured for other encodings or transports.\\\",\\nmetadata/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-exporter-otlp/index.json:6:    \\\"source-code-url\\\" : \\\"https://repo1.maven.org/maven2/io/opentelemetry/opentelemetry-exporter-otlp/$version$/opentelemetry-exporter-otlp-$version$-sources.jar\\\",\\nmetadata/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-exporter-otlp/index.json:7:    \\\"repository-url\\\" : \\\"https://github.com/open-telemetry/opentelemetry-java\\\",\\nmetadata/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-exporter-otlp/index.json:8:    \\\"test-code-url\\\" : \\\"https://github.com/open-telemetry/opentelemetry-java/tree/v$version$/exporters/otlp/all/src/test\\\",\\nmetadata/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-exporter-otlp/index.json:9:    \\\"documentation-url\\\" : \\\"https://github.com/open-telemetry/opentelemetry-java/blob/v$version$/exporters/otlp/all/README.md\\\",\\nmetadata/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-exporter-otlp/index.json:10:    \\\"description\\\" : \\\"Provides OpenTelemetry exporters that send traces and metrics to OTLP-compatible backends. This artifact packages the OTLP gRPC exporters used by Java applications to emit telemetry data to collectors and observability platforms.\\\",\\nmetadata/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-api-events/index.json:5:    \\\"source-code-url\\\" : \\\"https://repo.maven.apache.org/maven2/io/opentelemetry/opentelemetry-api-events/$version$/opentelemetry-api-events-$version$-sources.jar\\\",\\nmetadata/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-api-events/index.json:6:    \\\"repository-url\\\" : \\\"https://github.com/open-telemetry/opentelemetry-java\\\",\\nmetadata/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-api-events/index.json:7:    \\\"test-code-url\\\" : \\\"https://github.com/open-telemetry/opentelemetry-java/tree/v1.32.0/api/events/src/test\\\",\\nmetadata/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-api-events/index.json:8:    \\\"documentation-url\\\" : \\\"https://repo.maven.apache.org/maven2/io/opentelemetry/opentelemetry-api-events/$version$/opentelemetry-api-events-$version$-javadoc.jar\\\",\\nmetadata/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-api-events/index.json:9:    \\\"description\\\" : \\\"OpenTelemetry API Events provides the experimental Java API surface for creating and recording OpenTelemetry event telemetry. It supplies event-related interfaces and builders that integrate with the broader OpenTelemetry Java API so applications and instrumentation can emit structured events consistently.\\\",\\nmetadata/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-api-events/index.json:20:    \\\"source-code-url\\\" : \\\"https://repo.maven.apache.org/maven2/io/opentelemetry/opentelemetry-api-events/$version$/opentelemetry-api-events-$version$-sources.jar\\\",\\nmetadata/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-api-events/index.json:21:    \\\"repository-url\\\" : \\\"https://github.com/open-telemetry/opentelemetry-java\\\",\\nmetadata/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-api-events/index.json:22:    \\\"test-code-url\\\" : \\\"https://github.com/open-telemetry/opentelemetry-java/tree/v1.25.0/api/events/src/test\\\",\\nmetadata/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-api-events/index.json:23:    \\\"documentation-url\\\" : \\\"https://repo.maven.apache.org/maven2/io/opentelemetry/opentelemetry-api-events/$version$/opentelemetry-api-events-$version$-javadoc.jar\\\",\\nmetadata/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-api-events/index.json:24:    \\\"description\\\" : \\\"OpenTelemetry API Events provides the experimental Java API surface for creating and recording OpenTelemetry event telemetry. It supplies event-related interfaces and builders that integrate with the broader OpenTelemetry Java API so applications and instrumentation can emit structured events consistently.\\\",\\nmetadata/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-api/index.json:5:    \\\"source-code-url\\\" : \\\"https://repo.maven.apache.org/maven2/io/opentelemetry/opentelemetry-api/$version$/opentelemetry-api-$version$-sources.jar\\\",\\nmetadata/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-api/index.json:6:    \\\"repository-url\\\" : \\\"https://github.com/open-telemetry/opentelemetry-java\\\",\\nmetadata/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-api/index.json:7:    \\\"test-code-url\\\" : \\\"https://github.com/open-telemetry/opentelemetry-java/tree/v$version$/api/all/src/test/java\\\",\\nmetadata/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-api/index.json:8:    \\\"documentation-url\\\" : \\\"https://repo.maven.apache.org/maven2/io/opentelemetry/opentelemetry-api/$version$/opentelemetry-api-$version$-javadoc.jar\\\",\\nmetadata/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-api/index.json:9:    \\\"description\\\" : \\\"Provides the OpenTelemetry Java API for creating and interacting with telemetry such as traces, metrics, baggage, and context propagation in instrumentation code. It defines the core interfaces and data types used to record telemetry without including an SDK implementation.\\\",\\nmetadata/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-sdk-extension-autoconfigure-spi/index.json:5:    \\\"source-code-url\\\" : \\\"https://repo.maven.apache.org/maven2/io/opentelemetry/opentelemetry-sdk-extension-autoconfigure-spi/$version$/opentelemetry-sdk-extension-autoconfigure-spi-$version$-sources.jar\\\",\\nmetadata/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-sdk-extension-autoconfigure-spi/index.json:6:    \\\"repository-url\\\" : \\\"https://github.com/open-telemetry/opentelemetry-java\\\",\\nmetadata/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-sdk-extension-autoconfigure-spi/index.json:7:    \\\"test-code-url\\\" : \\\"https://github.com/open-telemetry/opentelemetry-java/tree/v$version$/sdk-extensions/autoconfigure-spi/src/test/java\\\",\\nmetadata/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-sdk-extension-autoconfigure-spi/index.json:8:    \\\"documentation-url\\\" : \\\"https://repo.maven.apache.org/maven2/io/opentelemetry/opentelemetry-sdk-extension-autoconfigure-spi/$version$/opentelemetry-sdk-extension-autoconfigure-spi-$version$-javadoc.jar\\\",\\nmetadata/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-sdk-extension-autoconfigure-spi/index.json:9:    \\\"description\\\" : \\\"This library defines service provider interfaces for customizing OpenTelemetry Java SDK auto-configuration. It lets extensions contribute configuration properties, resource providers, propagators, exporters, samplers, and tracer provider configuration hooks that are discovered by the autoconfigure module.\\\",\\nmetadata/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-exporter-logging/index.json:5:    \\\"source-code-url\\\" : \\\"https://repo.maven.apache.org/maven2/io/opentelemetry/opentelemetry-exporter-logging/$version$/opentelemetry-exporter-logging-$version$-sources.jar\\\",\\nmetadata/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-exporter-logging/index.json:6:    \\\"repository-url\\\" : \\\"